# NACAData.jl - AI Context File

## Project Overview
NACAData.jl is a Julia package providing fast aerodynamic performance lookup tables for NACA airfoils. It eliminates the need for computationally expensive panel methods by using pre-computed experimental data from NACA technical reports.

**Key Value Proposition:** 1000x faster than panel methods for standard NACA airfoil analysis.

## Project Status
- **Version:** 0.1.0 (MVP)
- **Status:** Development - Core functionality complete, needs real experimental data
- **License:** MIT
