## Performance Characteristics
- **Lookup time**: ~1ms (vs. seconds for panel methods)
- **Memory**: Minimal (pre-computed tables)
- **Accuracy**: Depends on source data quality and interpolation

## Common Issues
1. **Extrapolation warnings**: Occurs when Re or alpha outside data range
2. **Missing airfoil**: Check `list_available_airfoils()` for available codes
3. **Deprecation warning**: Known issue, will be fixed in next update

